div.span:
Determining collision side:
if moving actor right side is between static actor left/right
-> shift left: (2 * (s.x - (m.x + m.width)), 0)
if moving actor left side is between static actor left/right
-> shift right: (2 * ((s.x + s.width) - m.x), 0)
if moving actor bottom is between static actor top and bottom
-> shift up: (0, 2 * ((m.y + m.height) - s.y))
if moving actor top is between static actor top and bottom
-> shift down: (0, 2 * (m.y - (s.y + s.height)))
